  [Text] In Paris, President Francois Mitterrand has sent a 
message to Nelson Mandela. The French president spoke about a 
magnificent success for all of South Africa because it is one of 
courage and dialogue. France, Mitterrand added, will [quote] 
deploy all its effort so a live, open, and fully responsible 
democracy blooms in South Africa, end of quote. 

